data.description: This Beautiful 4 bedroom 2 Bath home has an open floor plan that features a large Kitchen which opens to an oversized Family room with built in media area.  The Kitchen has beautiful maple cabinets, a ceran Top range, a very large double door pantry, a breakfast nook, raised kitchen island bar and oversized tile flooring.  The Master bedroom has a sitting area and large walk in closet with upgrade shelving. Master bath is also tiled and very spacious with a large vanity/dressing area, 5' oval garden tub and large 4' separate shower.  The home has great curb appeal with the entry complimented by 18'' brick & quioned columns.   The Large foyer opens to formal dining area with access to kitchen and family room through a beautiful elliptical arched opening.
